<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{حِكْمَة بَالِغَة}</span> يَعْنِي: الْقُرْآن.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ محمدٌ:</span> <span class="c2">(حِكْمَةٌ بَالِغَة)</span> بِالرَّفْع على معنى: فَهُوَ حِكْمَة بَالِغَة.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{فَمَا تغن النّذر}</span> عَمَّن لَا يُؤمن<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>